{
  "stem": "25651.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For example, there was a street of pensioners in our hometown, and every Wednesday, we would-- my mother would cook a big bowl of soup-- potato soup, as a matter of fact.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I used to love potato soup.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it's sort of brown with-- you know, you make roux and become-- the soup becomes brown and it tastes after the roux.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it's full of onions and potatoes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But she made this big pot of soup, and three or four loaves of bread.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Czech loaves of bread are round.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I recall, when we were going to the street of the pensioners, that my brothers were carrying these loaves of bread under each arm.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the loaf of bread was too big for my underarm, you know, because I was still quite small.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, this is a very early memory in my hometown, how we walked this street.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The street was awful because it was all outside lavatories, very primitive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was no welfare in Czechoslovakia prewar, and they had very minute pensions.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The-- the hatters who were pensioned off from this factory all had-- you-- you know about Minamata disease?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Mercury poisoning?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Or hatters' disease-- you know, they were-- they were mad.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's sort-- it's a sort of-- they shake and they can't find their center of gravity.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There's a lot of drunkenness in Czechoslovakia, anyway.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So in the street, the pension would be always taken by the men, and the men would use it for drink.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, on the day that it was paid, the men would get drunk, and then, the whole week, the family didn't have anything to live on, except on Wednesdays when-- when we came.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my mother organized some other women, also, to do the same thing.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
